<p>The BigDFT project was an European project (FP6-NEST) from 2005 to 2008.</p>

<p>Four institutions were implicated in the BigDFT project (version < 1.1):</p>
<ul>
  <li>Commissariat a l'Énergie Atomique (T. Deutsch),</li>
  <li>University of Basel (S. Goedecker),</li>
  <li>Université catholique de Louvain (X. Gonze),</li>
  <li>Christian-Albrechts Universität zu Kiel (R. Schneider).</li>
</ul>

<p>From 2010, three laboratories are contributing: L_Sim (CEA), UNIBAS and ESRF.</p>

